data.description: This inviting single-story residence is move-in ready and rests upon a spacious lot, nestled in the highly desirable Canyon Hills community. It enjoys a prime location, within a short stroll of an elementary school, parks, and a pool thats fells like you are at a resort. The interior boasts an open and luminous floor plan, adorned with new luxury vinyl flooring, high baseboards, and barn doors that gracefully enclose the generous den, which could effortlessly transform into a fourth bedroom. The backyard is an entertainer's dream, graced by a generous covered patio and elegant hardscaping. The kitchen is equipped with an island, and granite countertops. This is an opportunity you won't want to miss!
